'''皮耶羅·迪·科西莫'''（'''Piero di Cosimo'''，1462年1月2日<ref>After much uncertainty, Piero's birth date was identified in the parish records of San Lorenzo by Dennis Geronimus, "The Birth Date, Early Life, and Career of Piero di Cosimo", ''The Art Bulletin'' '''82'''.1 (March 2000:164-170); Geronimus was able to rely on the consistency of Lorenzo di Piero d'Antonio's reports of his children's ages at the ''[[catasto|catasti]]'' of 1469 and 1480, and a new database of Florentine baptismal records.</ref> – 1522年4月12日），亦稱'''皮耶羅·迪·洛倫佐'''（'''Piero di Lorenzo'''），是[[意大利文藝復興|意大利文藝復興]]時期的一位畫家。<ref name="collier">{{cite encyclopedia |last=Godfrey |first=F.M. |editor=William D. Halsey |encyclopedia=Collier's Encyclopedia |title=Piero di Cosmio |year=1976 |publisher=Macmillan Educational Corporation |volume=19 |location=New York |page=42 }}</ref>

==生平==
科西莫出生於[[佛羅倫薩|佛羅倫薩]]，是一位金匠的兒子。他曾受到[[科西莫·羅塞利|科西莫·羅塞利]]的指點，他的名字也是從老師那裡取來的。1481年在[[西斯廷禮拜堂|西斯廷禮拜堂]]協助老師進行創作。後來他自己也成為了一名著名畫家。[[喬爾喬·瓦薩里|喬爾喬·瓦薩里]]為他在《[[藝苑名人傳|藝苑名人傳]]》留下了一席之地。<ref>{{cite book|last=Fermor|first= Sharon|title=Piero di Cosimo: Fiction, Invention, and Fantasia|publisher=Reaktion Books|year=1997|pages=7–9 and ff}}</ref>

瓦薩里給出的科西莫逝世時間為1521年，包括《[[大英百科全書|大英百科全書]]》等的許多文獻中都採取此說。<ref>{{cite encyclopedia | title = Piero Di Cosimo | encyclopedia = Encyclopædia Britannica | volume =  | pages =  | publisher = Encyclopædia Britannica Online | year = 2006 | url = http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9059972 | accessdate = 2006-10-28 | archive-date = 2020-04-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200403214127/https://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9059972 | dead-url = no }}</ref>  但後來有證據顯示其正確的逝世時間為1522年4月12日。<ref name="waldman">{{cite journal | last = Waldman | first = Louis Alexander | authorlink = | coauthors = | title = Fact, Fiction, Hearsay: Notes on Vasari's Life of Piero di Cosimo | journal = The Art Bulletin | volume =  82 | issue = 1 | pages = 171–9 | publisher = The Art Bulletin, Vol. 82, No. 1|date=March 2000 | jstor = 3051370| doi = 10.2307/3051370 }}</ref>

==逸聞==
傳聞科西莫害怕打雷，還有恐火癥，因此從來不做飯，只依靠煮雞蛋為生。他在為他的作品準備材料時會順便準備50個煮雞蛋。<ref>[http://www.oxfordartonline.com/subscriber/article/grove/art/T067492 Original information sourced from: William Griswold. "Piero di Cosimo."] Grove Art Online. Oxford Art Online. Oxford University Press. Web. 5 Aug. 2014.</ref> 他拒絕清理畫室，也不修剪自家果園裡果樹。因此瓦薩里評價他“相對人類而言更像是一匹野獸”。

